/// (3) Label the pixels as follows:
/// 1  4  7
/// 2  5  8
/// 3  6  9
/// Read the data incrementally across the image and unroll
/// the loop.<para/>
/// 
/// (4) This runs at about 45 Mpix/sec on a 3 GHz processor.
///  </summary>
