/// (2) This can be used to generate 'captcha's, which are somewhat
/// randomly distorted images of text.  A typical set of parameters
/// for a captcha are:
/// xmag = 4.0 ymag = 6.0
/// xfreq = 0.10 yfreq = 0.13
/// nx = 3 ny = 3
/// Other examples can be found in prog/warptest.c.
///  </summary>
